"1  roasting chicken, about 5 lbs.","1  lemon, halved","2 tablespoons unsalted butter, softened","  Salt and pepper","2  leeks, dark green leaves trimmed, halved lengthwise, cut into 2-inch lengths","2  carrots, cut into 1-inch pieces","2  parsnips, cut into 1-inch pieces, thick ends halved","2  small white turnips, peeled and halved","6  small red potatoes, halved","2  shallots, halved","2  sprigs fresh thyme","2 tablespoons olive oil","1/2 cup low-sodium chicken broth"